{
  "texts": [
    "This capability is essential for proactive fault detection, allowing the NDT to identify issues before they escalate.",
    "The healing models are constructed based on the detected anomalies that can determine the best possible corrective policies for the network.",
    "These models are designed to address various fault scenarios such as link failures, node outages, and performance degradation.",
    "The generated healing actions must be prevalidated within the DTN.",
    "After the actions are validated, they are delivered to the physical network."
  ]
}